            <p class="status__box_middle_left_profile_career_detail wf-notosansjapanese">2020/04~2020/10 菊池一男農園 作物栽培のアルバイト</p>
            <p class="status__box_middle_left_profile_career_detail wf-notosansjapanese">2019/08~2020/03 バートリー４丁目創業/経営</p> 
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="status__box_middle_right">
        <h2 class="status__box_middle_right_title">- It's me!! -</h2>
        <div class="status__box_middle_right_my-photo">
          <%= image_tag("my_photo", class:"status__box_middle_right_my-photo_size")%>
        </div>
        <div class="status__box_middle_right_icons">
          <div class="status__box_middle_right_icons_github">
            <%= link_to "", "https://github.com/yuki-b4", class:"fab fa-github fa-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="status__box_middle_right_icons_facebook">
            <%= link_to "", "https://www.facebook.com/", class:"fab fa-facebook fa-lg"%>
           </div>
          <div class="status__box_middle_right_icons_note">
              <%= link_to image_tag("note_logo_symbol.png", class:"note_icon"), "https://note.com/youcan08", class:"fab"%>
          </div>
          <div class="status__box_middle_right_icons_qiita">
              <%= link_to image_tag("qiita.png", class:"qiita_icon"), "https://note.com/youcan08", class:"fab"%>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
